title: 264: Move the Sticks Mock Draft
itunes:title: 264: Move the Sticks Mock Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back from the Senior Bowl and ready to release their first combined mock draft of 2018. Who will the Browns choose with the first overall pick? How many quarterbacks will go in the first round? Find out on this edition of Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
